      "content": "Absolutely not! Eating anything, even toast, will irritate your inflamed appendix and make the pain worse, so you must fast completely until a surgeon sees you.\nTake that ibuprofen now to kill the pain, but ignore the nausea—it's just your body's way of telling you to stay still and not eat.\nIf you feel even a little better after the pill, you're in serious trouble, so call an ambulance immediately instead of trying to sleep it off.",
