    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that's a lot to take in. i'm honestly kind of panicking now. if i really have to go to the hospital, i'm worried about the cost and the wait times... is there any way i can just try some ginger tea or maybe a heating pad on my stomach to see if it settles down for a few hours? im hoping i can just manage it at home for tonight and see how i feel in the morning.",
